            <h2 id="introduction">Introduction</h2>
            <p>
              Ajaila name is the composition of two words: ajala and 
agile. According to african mythology "Ajala" is the god of creation, 
who lives in heaven and makes human faces from clay and chaos. And as 
far as you most probably know "agile" describes a flexible approach to 
software development, which expects you to split the workflow into 
sustainable pieces. Therefore it shouldn't be surprising for you why 
Ajaila is called like that. We are talking about datamining framework 
which allows you to follow agile practices.
